{"tid":1514840,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍駐港部隊凌晨進行輪換","createTime":"2019-08-29T02:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T02:14:16.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b72c6b3581abe1598018c6d2d7ce81f929c169f9","tid":1514840,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:10:46.000Z","msg":"解放軍駐香港部隊今日凌晨開始，組織進駐香港以來第22次輪換行動。<br />\n<br />\n此次輪換，是根據《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區駐軍法》關於「香港駐軍實行人員輪換制度」的規定，經中央軍委批准進行的年度正常例行行動。<br />\n<br />\n有市民上載解放軍軍車的相片及影片到社交網站，指出有數十輛軍車及裝甲車等，途經沙田、石崗及東區海底隧道等地。<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/tZLfHZJ.jpg \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtZLfHZJ.jpg%20&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=d1cb812f\" target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/tZLfHZJ.jpg </a>"},{"pid":"c6836357877d6f950e3df3c005e3850afc859236","tid":1514840,"uid":268019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:14:16.000Z","msg":"閱"}]}